TICKETS NOW ON SALE! 
We have put an extremely limited amount of tickets on sales during this presale period. The presale will end on at midnight on Friday, January 13, 2023. 

TICKET BREAKDOWN 
$250.00 - ALL ACCESS PASS 
Front row ticket to every show all weekend long (premium seating)
Early entry into venue- Director's Cocktail Reception (Friday night)
Complimentary Grab & Go Breakfast (Saturday morning)
Access to Director''s Suite throughout the day with complimentary snacks and beverages
Goodie bag filled with sweet treats
Souvenir Copy of Art & Beauty Magazine

$135.00 - THREE SHOW PACK
One front row ticket to 3 shows of your choosing. Simply purchase the pack and then email beautytiseverywhere@gmail.com with your 3 showtimes. 

$95 - TWO SHOW PACK 
One front row ticket to 2 shows of your choosing. Simply purchase the pack and then email beautytiseverywhere@gmail.com with your 2 showtimes. 

$50 - VIP SINGLE TICKETS 
Select the show time of your choice. 

HOW TO BOOK YOUR TICKETS:
Visit: https://www.beautyitseverywhere.org/shop 
Type in code: NYFW2023 
Select the item you want and add it to your cart 
Check out and submit payment 

HOW TO CLAIM:
Badges (All Access only) and wristbands will be available for pick up starting on Friday, February 10, 2023 at 4PM outside the Crystal Ballroom. You will also be able to pick up tickets at registration Saturday morning and right before the start of each show. You must bring a copy of your receipt and photo id in order to claim tickets. All sales are final. No refunds or exchanges 

MODELS ARE NOT REQUIRED TO PURCHASE A TICKET TO SEE ANY OF THE SHOWS PRESENTED BY BEAUTY IT'S EVERYWHERE. SEATING IS LIMITED AND ON A FIRST COME FIRST SERVE SET UP. LANYARD REQUIRED FOR ENTRY. THERE IS NO GUARANTEE YOU WILL BE ADMITTED INTO THE SHOW.
